headline: Hewlett Packard Enterprise (HPE) Added to JPMorgan Focus List After Juniper Deal
summary: Hewlett-Packard Enterprise Company (NYSE:HPE) is one of the AI Stocks on Wall Street’s Radar. On July 17, JPMorgan added HPE to its focus list, stating that shares of Hewlett Packard Enterprise have more room to run. The stock was rated “Overweight” from a Not Rated designation, with a December 2026 price target of $30 on the […]

headline: Trump's antitrust cops are OK with new mergers. Old tech monopolies, not so much.
summary: President Trump's antitrust cops are so far friendlier about mergers than their predecessors, but they are refusing to let up on one prominent priority of the Biden administration: monopoly prosecutions of the nation's best-known tech giants.
